history.content: I'm in 105 right now. The first couple labs are doable, but the rest required outside time from lab due to reviewing the prelab with the GSI in order to understand how to do even do the lab. The last two labs definitely require multiple lab periods to complete even if you used the entire lab.

I really want to take EE 105 next semester, but I have conflicts with each lab section. For almost all of these, I only have one hour of overlap. One or two people I know mentioned having an hour conflict but being able to still do all the labs in time each week (with some additional outside work), but this was before 105 was changed to match 16. Would it be doable now?
history.subject: EE 105 Lab Conflicts
